==Trivia==
*Demonic gorillas are similar to the {{RSL|Tormented demon|tormented demons}} of ''RuneScape 3''; both use all three forms of [[combat]], [[protection prayers]] and drop items that are used to create more powerful equipment.
*Demonic gorillas' prayers were slightly changed several days after release due to several glitches happening with specific weapons, notably the [[Saradomin godsword]].

